Job Description
Job Purpose
You will be part of the Group Data Management & Governance Office, specifically in the area of Enterprise Data Governance.
You will be leading a team of data governance officers to protect the privacy of all individuals and enhance the value of our data asset. You will have to design and establish data governance programs and initiatives to steer, drive the organization towards data driven, and enable innovations while preserving the confidentiality of data.
The Job
Partner with senior management team, business leaders and technology department to develop and drive an enterprise-wide Data Governance strategy, operationalize the data management policies, procedures and standards;
