Steer the BU & SU to achieve their goals in a compliance, effective and efficient manner using data and technology;
Strategize to shift mindset and embed data obligations and accountabilities into everyone??s day to day activities, and to develop self-service data culture to improve overall business efficiency;
Design and lead the team to implement data governance programs and initiatives to ensure compliance with regulations, raise the value of data and enable data democratization;
Perform oversight on all data governance programs and initiatives to ensure alignment and effective implementation across the Group;
Lead the secretariat team to support Data Governance Committee and Data Governance Working Group;
Design and implement programs and initiatives to raise the overall data literacy and data control obligations across the Group to enable intelligent workforce and minimize data incidents;
Design, develop and maintain all data governance artefacts (e.g. framework, policies, standards and guidelines) to ensure compliance with regulations, relevancy and up-to-date to meet the organization??s strategic objectives and business needs;
